---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About | FreeOnlyFanz"
  description="FreeOnlyFanz is an independent 18+ directory of curated creator picks. Learn who we are and what we do."
  canonicalPath="/about/"
>
  <article class="info-page container">
    <header class="info-page-header">
      <p class="info-eyebrow">About</p>
      <h1>About FreeOnlyFanz</h1>
    </header>
    <div class="info-page-body">
      <p>
        FreeOnlyFanz is an independent discovery site for adults. We highlight curated creator picks—mostly free pages and
        free-trial pages—so you can browse in one place instead of digging through random lists.
      </p>
      <p>
        We are not run by any creator platform. We do not speak for creators, and we do not guarantee how third-party pages
        behave after you leave this site.
      </p>
      <p>
        Some outbound links may be sponsored or affiliate links. That helps keep the lights on; it does not change the fact
        that we are a small, independent directory.
      </p>
      <p class="note">18+ only. If you are not an adult in your region, please leave.</p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
